stm32mp2-gpu-userspace for Debian/Ubuntu
==========================================

This package contains the ARM64 STM32MP2-specific ST Vivante GCNANO user-space
payload extracted from:

  @INSTALLER@

The vendor libraries are kept under:

  @LIBDIR@

and are activated system-wide with an ld.so configuration file. This may take
precedence over Mesa implementations of EGL, GLES and related APIs. Remove the
package, or remove its ld.so configuration file and run `ldconfig`, to revert.

The package includes OpenCL and Vulkan ICD descriptors only when the extracted
payload contains corresponding vendor libraries.

Upstream commit: @UPSTREAM_COMMIT@
